id: pmc-dkmm
title: Adopt scoped renderer ownership for changelog JSON output
description: Migrate pm-changelog's toon/json overrides to the pm SDK scoped renderer ownership contract so isolated package doctor can prove the callbacks only own changelog command results.
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-07-23T15:06:24.649Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-24T06:41:53.586Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-24T06:41:53.585Z"
author: claude-code-agent
acceptance_criteria: Both renderer registrations declare changelog command ownership and a RenderedCommandResult discriminator; unrelated results bypass the callback; package tests and isolated doctor pass against the scoped-renderer SDK.
resolution: "toon+json renderers registered via api.registerRenderer with an ownership object {commands:['changelog generate','changelog export'], resultDiscriminator:isRenderedCommandResult}, cast-free and type-checked against the 2026.7.24 signature; renderedCommandResult now rejects non-serializable values."
expected_result: Both registrations declare changelog command ownership + a RenderedCommandResult discriminator; unrelated results bypass the callback; tests and isolated doctor pass against the scoped-renderer SDK.
actual_result: "149/149 tests pass (incl. ownership-metadata contract coverage); changelog:check up to date; pack:dry-run clean; 0 prod vulnerabilities; isolated package doctor warning-free on pm-cli 2026.7.24."
